  :motoi-relevant-chapters-est 700
  :estimated-pairs-total 4900
  :confidence "medium — chapter counts inferred from directory listing; actual code-block density needs a script pass"
  :extraction-safety "Read-only. Book files are canonical prose that Alfred authors. Extraction produces derivative training data, never edits."
